  "body": "I noticed there is a new `--remotedb` argument in cli, and found the PR https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/24836\r\n\r\nI'm quite interested in this idea of remotedb, because I'm looking for a way to scale my geth rpc service without too much additional storage costs, and remotedb looks a perfect solution for that. Though due to lack of documents I'm not sure if remotedb can be used in that way.\r\n\r\n",
